summary: Simply adds a new black leather armor set without replacing the original.
descriptionHtml:
Simply adds a new black leather armor set without replacing the original. Stats are the same, but the set also requires Frostbite Venom to craft, as venom has necrotic properties that can blacken flesh. Tested with males and females of all vanilla races with vanilla bodies. Will not appear in vendor lists or as gear for random NPCs.

Texture retrieved from [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5063/?]Leather Armor Alternative Textures[/url] by [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/1814616/?]exray catt[/url] using the 2048 version.

This is my first mod so if it appears I\'m doing something wrong please let me know.
author: DissidentRage
